<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Eshop Seller Account Activation</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      min-width: 100%;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #222;
    }
    a {
      color: #0070f3;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    p {
      margin: 0 0 20px;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 6px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .email-header {
      background-color: #0070f3;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .email-body {
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .email-footer {
      padding: 16px 24px;
      background-color: #fafafa;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #555;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      color: #333;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Welcome to Eshop Seller Portal!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for registering as a seller with Eshop. To activate your seller account, please use the OTP below:</p>

      <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>

      <p>This OTP is valid for <strong>5 minutes</strong>. Enter it on the seller activation page to complete your setup.</p>

      <p>If you did not sign up to become a seller, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>
        Need help? Contact us at
        <a href="mailto:ansarishahalam855@gmail.com">ansarishahalam855@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
